@startuml Sequence_UC07
title UC-07: Kelola Produk dan Komposisi

actor "Bagian Inventori" as User
participant "Halaman Produk\n(livewire/product)" as View
participant "Product\\Form\n(Livewire)" as Component
participant "Product Model" as ProductModel
participant "ProductComposition Model" as CompositionModel
participant "OtherCost Model" as CostModel
participant "Category Model" as CategoryModel
database "Database" as DB

User -> View: Membuka /produk → klik Tambah Produk
View -> Component: mount()
Component -> DB: SELECT categories, materials, units, type_costs
DB --> Component: Data referensi
Component --> View: Tampil form produk

== Tambah Produk ==
User -> View: Isi nama, metode, pcs, harga,\nkomposisi, biaya lalu simpan
View -> Component: save()
Component -> Component: validate(['name'=>'required',\n'method'=>'required|array|min:1',\n'pcs'=>'required|min:1',\n'image'=>'nullable|max:2048'])
alt Validasi gagal
  Component --> View: Pesan kesalahan
else Berhasil
  Component -> ProductModel: Product::create([...])
  ProductModel -> DB: INSERT INTO products
  DB --> ProductModel: Product baru

  Component -> CategoryModel: Sync product_categories pivot
  CategoryModel -> DB: INSERT INTO product_categories

  loop Setiap item komposisi
    Component -> CompositionModel: ProductComposition::create([...])
    CompositionModel -> DB: INSERT INTO product_compositions
  end

  loop Setiap biaya tambahan
    Component -> CostModel: OtherCost::create([...])
    CostModel -> DB: INSERT INTO other_costs
  end

  Component -> ProductModel: Hitung ulang $product->capital
  ProductModel -> DB: UPDATE products SET capital = ?

  Component --> View: Notifikasi sukses → redirect daftar
end

== Ubah Komposisi ==
User -> View: Buka rincian produk → ubah jumlah bahan → simpan
View -> Component: updateComposition($compositionId, $qty)
Component -> CompositionModel: ProductComposition::find($id)->update(['material_quantity'=>$qty])
CompositionModel -> DB: UPDATE product_compositions
Component -> ProductModel: Hitung ulang modal
ProductModel -> DB: UPDATE products SET capital = ?
Component --> View: Notifikasi sukses

== Tambah Biaya Tambahan ==
User -> View: Pilih jenis biaya, isi nominal → simpan
View -> Component: saveCost()
Component -> CostModel: OtherCost::create(['product_id'=>..., 'type_cost_id'=>..., 'price'=>...])
CostModel -> DB: INSERT INTO other_costs
Component -> ProductModel: Hitung ulang modal
Component --> View: Notifikasi sukses

@enduml
